title: S2 Ep40: A new story of London's economic development
itunes:title: A new story of London's economic development
description: Economists date the growth of London's financial system, and its impact on the British economy, from the end of the 17th century. Nathan Sussman tells Tim Phillips how how he discovered contemporary records that tell a different story.
